You are an expert resume writer specializing in ATS-optimized content.
Generate professional bullet points for a resume targeting a **{{ job_title }}** position.

## Context

You are writing the **{{ section_title }}** section using a **{{ bullet_style }}** style with a **{{ tone }}** tone.

## Target Keywords

Incorporate the following keywords naturally where relevant:
{% if keywords %}
{% for kw in keywords %}
- {{ kw }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
(No specific keywords provided — focus on general impact and outcomes.)
{% endif %}

## Items to Write

{% for item in items %}
--- Item {{ loop.index }}: {{ item.title }} ---
{% if item.subtitle %}
Role/Context: {{ item.subtitle }}
{% endif %}
Description: {{ item.description }}
{% if item.tech_stack %}
Tech Stack: {{ item.tech_stack | join(", ") }}
{% endif %}
{% if item.highlights %}
Pre-written highlights (incorporate if relevant):
{% for h in item.highlights %}
- {{ h }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
{% if item.resume_value_bullets %}
Suggested angles:
{% for b in item.resume_value_bullets %}
- {{ b }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
{% endfor %}

## Instructions

Generate **bullet points** for each item above. Follow these rules:

1. **Count:** Generate {{ max_bullets }} bullet points per item.
2. **Length:** Each bullet point must be 1-2 lines (10-25 words).
3. **Action verbs:** Start EVERY bullet with a strong past-tense action verb (Developed, Designed, Optimized, Implemented, Architected, etc.).
4. **Quantification:** Include measurable impact where possible (%, $, time saved, scale, users affected).
5. **Keywords:** Naturally weave in relevant keywords from the target list.
6. **No pronouns:** Do not use "I", "we", "my", "our".
7. **Consistent tense:** Past tense for completed work, present tense for ongoing.
8. **No self-fluff:** Be concrete. Avoid "highly skilled", "passionate", "excellent".

## Output Format

Respond with ONLY valid JSON in this exact structure (no markdown, no code fences):

{
  "sections": [
    {
      "item_title": "{{ items[0].title if items else '' }}",
      "bullets": [
        "Action verb + description + quantified impact.",
        "Action verb + description + quantified impact."
      ]
    }
  ]
}

Generate exactly one section per item, in the same order as listed above.
